This is Perl module Infra.

INSTALLATION

    % git clone https://riywo@github.com/riywo/Infra.git
    % cd Infra
    % perl script/setup/infra_setup.pl
    % perl script/setup/maatkit_setup.pl
    % source ~/.bashrc

USAGE

    % vi config/development.pl
    % infra_mysql -e "show databases"

SEE ALSO

    https://github.com/riywo/Infra/wiki

riywo
